<item>
            <title>[HBASE-1126] Enable choice of codec; i.e. at a minimum enable LZO COMPRESSION support</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-1126</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It would be interesting to see the performance of lzo compressed Column Families Vs Normal ZlibBlock Compression. Based on some very preliminary performance profiling that I have done, as long as the cells are of reasonable size ( &amp;gt; 4k ), the zlib compression really dominates the overhead in random read/scanning situations.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;All&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
        <key id="12412394">HBASE-1126</key>
            <summary>Enable choice of codec; i.e. at a minimum enable LZO COMPRESSION support</summary>
